        Description copied from interface: RandomOutput

        Specified by:
        getExistingForFilters in interface RandomOutput
        Parameters:
        filters - An iterable collection of filters, where each filter is a Row that the existing records must exactly match all values on. This is typically used for key lookups, where the iterable collection is a batch of keys (each defined as a Row).
